comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-24T08:42:52.228Z",codex-gpt5,"Continuation: PR #353 is still open with failing Gates (coverage) and Gates (smokes) on head 5bd07b82. Reopening/continuing the existing TypeScript-only extension loading lineage instead of creating a duplicate item. Root failure: beads/todos package commands cannot resolve runtime.ts from the package-first installed path; review follow-up also requires tsconfig.examples allowImportingTsExtensions, scaffold engines.node >=22.18.0, Node 22 TS-loading smoke coverage, and pm-frou metadata reconciliation via pm."
  "2026-06-24T09:14:36.493Z",codex-gpt5,"Evidence: PR #353 follow-up fixes are implemented and locally verified. Fixed package runtime-loader missing-module classification so missing dependencies inside discovered runtime.ts are rethrown instead of being swallowed as a missing runtime. Added Node 22 dist smoke for TS package runtime loading, tsconfig.examples allowImportingTsExtensions, scaffold package engines.node >=22.18.0, and pm-frou metadata reconciliation. Focused checks passed: gen-package-runtime-loaders --check; runtime-loader/scaffold/CI contract tests 30 passed; CI failure slice 3 passed; pnpm dogfood:package-first 88 commands ok. Full gates passed: pnpm typecheck; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage = 248 files, 4993 tests, 100/100/100/100; quality:static; quality:docs-skills; contracts:check; changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog latest npm version 2026.6.20; security:scan; pnpm audit --audit-level low; version:check; compatibility-check; npm pack --dry-run; pm health --check-only; pnpm smoke:external-packages tested 10 packages with 0 failures; pnpm release:gates passed end to end. Manual temp-dir smoke passed at /tmp/tmp.YPXDQmEAE4 using isolated PM_PATH and PM_GLOBAL_PATH: init, create, install beads/todos one-at-a-time, beads import, todos export, scaffold/install starter-extension, run starter extension ping, extension doctor strict summary with 3 active runtimes and 0 warnings, health ok. GitHub reports checked: PR #353 had stale failures on previous head; open issue #348 is related to unsupported Node 20 nightly and is linked to pm-2kkl; branch nightly matrix no longer includes Node 20. Dependabot/code-scanning/secret-scanning alert APIs returned 404/not enabled or not visible to token, while local secret scan and pnpm audit are green. Sentry/telemetry gate checked unbrained/pm-cli over 14 days: 0 critical, 0 high, 11 expected CLI-error issues ignored, telemetry finish error rate 0.86%, missing error-code rows 0."
